The paper deals with the problem of pilot contamination in massive MIMO systems, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and networked systems (cs.NI). The proposed approach also involves location-based methods, which can be categorized under systems and control (cs.SY). The paper specifically focuses on multi-user multi-cell scenarios, which is a topic related to machine learning (cs.MM) and large-scale data analysis (cs.LG).
